50|$|Torpedo {{countermeasures}} can be towed or free. An early {{example was}} the German Sieglinde device while the Bold was a chemical device. A widely used US device was the towed AN/SLQ-25 Nixie while Mobile submarine simulator (MOSS) {{was a free}} device. A modern alternative to the Nixie system is the UK Royal Navy S2170 Surface Ship <b>Torpedo</b> <b>Defence</b> system.|$|R
